I know what I say may seem unreasonable to you.

40
00:02:37,330 --> 00:02:40,060
I also shouldn't pressure you like this.

41
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:44,570
But… but he is my brother.

42
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,480
Just see it as my asking you to do me a favor.

43
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:51,430
Could you impersonate CEO one more time?

44
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:59,210
Are you kidding me? Impossible!

45
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:04,890
William Yi can live without me, but not without Yi Shan.

46
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:08,320
Even if he recovers, when he finds out<br>the CEO position has been replaced,

47
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,620
he won't be able to live with that.

48
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:15,010
Ah Bin, I beg you.

49
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:16,710
Please...

50
00:03:21,390 --> 00:03:22,860
No.

51
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:26,690
Can you please stop pressuring me?

52
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:39,290
Look at the way he is now. He really is very sick.

53
00:03:39,290 --> 00:03:42,040
I don't want to! Why should I?

54
00:03:46,690 --> 00:03:49,400
Then do you want to take a look at my mom's blood stains?

55
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:54,290
What wrong has my mother done?

56
00:03:58,890 --> 00:04:01,720
She is still in a coma. Don't you know?

57
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:05,190
She is not better off than your brother.

58
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:17,020
I'm very sorry.

59
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:20,420
I really can't help you.

60
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:40,610
<i>CEO, this way please.</i>

61
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:48,520
Not yet. Not quite yet.

62
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:54,180
The order for you to be the interim CEO<br>will be issued sooner or later.

63
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:56,910
It will surely happen soon.

64
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:07,380
By the way, CEO Zhao

65
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:10,450
how would you like your office decorated?

66
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:13,820
Just give me an order, I will hire a designer<br>to take care of it right away.

67
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:32,510
Haste can make a person blind.

68
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:38,450
Once I get the last straw that'll break the camel's back,

69
00:05:38,450 --> 00:05:41,880
my plan will not be like this anymore.

70
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:46,580
I've endured everything for so long.<br>Do you think I can't wait another day or two?

71
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:51,920
Aren't we waiting for the board of directors<br>to have a vote in the board meeting?

72
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:57,180
All the directors are on your side, so the camel has already fallen. Why do we need the last straw?

73
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:07,820
Seriously, you...

74
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:14,140
With a brain like yours, how am I going to make you<br>the head of the secretarial department?

75
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,930
CEO, you mean...

76
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:36,490
I just took the medicine. Ask Maka Long to get the car ready.

77
00:06:36,490 --> 00:06:38,160
I have to go to work.

78
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,740
- Brother..<br>- Ok, ok.

79
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:45,070
I will call Maka Long right away for you.

80
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,450
Did he lose his temper again?

81
00:06:55,450 --> 00:06:59,240
He yelled at all the doctors and the nurses just now.<br>But at least he was willing to take the medicine.

82
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:02,260
Otherwise the doctor might suggest to tie him up again.

83
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:07,040
Are you ok? Your clothes are all wet.

84
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:10,580
I'm fine.<br>Oh, don't be mad at him.

85
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:14,810
The doctor said, at first, because his mental state<br> is still unstable, so the dosage is higher.

86
00:07:14,810 --> 00:07:18,450
Very soon when the drug begins to take effect,

87
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:20,890
his mood will be more stable.

88
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:27,550
You've done a lot these days.

89
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:33,150
William is suffering more than me.

90
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,610
William, lie down for awhile.

91
00:07:41,610 --> 00:07:44,400
I will let you know when Maka Long is here.

92
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:59,410
Be good and lie here.<br>I need to go home now,

93
00:07:59,410 --> 00:08:01,700
but I'll be back soon.

94
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:04,650
Don't worry.

95
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:12,900
You have to take good care of yourself.

96
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:15,590
You must be exhausted.

97
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:17,890
Take a rest after you get home.

98
00:08:17,890 --> 00:08:22,780
No. I will be right back after I change my clothes.<br>It won't take long.

99
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:44,210
Brother. Take a nap.

100
00:08:44,210 --> 00:08:46,550
Don't think about the company, ok?

101
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:54,490
Have you told the board of directors

102
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,680
that I can go back to work now?

103
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:07,730
Brother, I'm sorry.

104
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:12,590
None of them wanted to see me.

105
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:15,280
There is nothing I can do to help.

106
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:19,620
I don't think I can protect your CEO position.

107
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:22,090
I'm sorry.

108
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:47,470
Mom, God did hear what we were asking him.

109
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:53,220
There is a chance Mei Village might not get torn down.

110
00:09:55,610 --> 00:10:00,170
Dad's sea will still belong to all of us.

111
00:10:00,170 --> 00:10:04,580
But… you need to get better soon.

112
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:10,190
Without you at home, no one nags me.

113
00:10:10,190 --> 00:10:12,600
I am too lazy to clean up now.

114
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:15,450
Our house is almost like a pile of garbage!

115
00:10:15,450 --> 00:10:17,550
Do you hear me?

116
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:30,330
Also, didn't you, Uncle and Aunt Ah-Zhu

117
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:33,710
plan to take a trip to Hokkaido during the New Year?

118
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:36,880
If you don't get better soon,

119
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:39,450
you'll miss the tour.

120
00:10:39,450 --> 00:10:42,010
Don't complain to me when that happens,

121
00:10:42,010 --> 00:10:46,620
or ask me to take you there instead.<br>You hear me?

122
00:11:09,190 --> 00:11:10,790
Mom!

123
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,660
Did your hand just move?

124
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:17,380
Move your fingers one more time.

125
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:23,980
I saw your hand moved. Do that again!

126
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:35,220
Ms. Lai Yu Xia, do you hear me?

127
00:11:36,430 --> 00:11:38,770
Move your fingers again for me.

128
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:55,090
Mom!

129
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:11,390
Mom… I knew you could hear me.

130
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:26,360
<i>Come out with me for a second.</i>

131
00:12:30,780 --> 00:12:33,480
Is it really a good idea to give him those books<br>about bipolar disorder?

132
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:36,790
I think my brother needs to face his problem directly.

133
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:39,920
That's the only way to solve the current difficult situation.

134
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:42,830
Exactly what else can we do to help William?

135
00:12:42,830 --> 00:12:45,450
Every time when I remember it was my dad<br>who made William the way he is now,

136
00:12:45,450 --> 00:12:47,630
I feel everything is my fault.

137
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:49,630
- I have done wrong to William…<br>- Katy Zhao.

138
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:51,600
Please don't look at it this way.

139
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:55,590
Your dad was only the last flash point.<br>As the doctor has said,

140
00:12:55,590 --> 00:12:59,290
the cause of bipolar can be very complicated.<br>I think...

141
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:01,920
this is a test for my brother.

142
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:05,980
Perhaps if he can get through it this time,<br>we'll all learn to understand ourselves better,

143
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:08,170
and to understand others better.

144
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:12,270
But I am very worried. I worry whether or not

145
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:14,970
William will dislike me because of my dad.

146
00:13:14,970 --> 00:13:18,240
He won't. He is not that kind of person.

147
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:22,510
Besides, you've done so much for him.<br>I'm sure he knows.

148
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:23,860
OK?

149
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,790
What the heck!

150
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:38,670
I don't believe any of these. Take them all away!

151
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,940
Where is Maka Long?

152
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:42,900
Why hasn't he come to tell me what's going on in the company?

153
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:46,570
Brother, could you let go of the company just for now?

154
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:50,130
You must face your illness first.<br>Only then we can really solve the problem.

155
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:52,800
Besides, the doctor has said

156
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:55,290
bipolar is something that might stay with you<br>for the rest of your life.

157
00:13:55,290 --> 00:13:57,490
Yi Xin!

158
00:13:57,490 --> 00:14:00,840
Why should I let a incompetent doctor decide my future?

159
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:04,280
I am only here to rest. I am fine!

160
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:06,760
I must go back to the office. I am going to Yi Shan.

161
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:08,540
Ok. I understand.

162
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:10,890
Let's rest a few more days then we'll go home, ok?

163
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:14,210
The weather is nice today. Take me out to get some sunlight.

164
00:14:14,210 --> 00:14:16,170
Have a walk with me, ok?

165
00:14:16,170 --> 00:14:18,810
Come!

166
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:31,700
"A bigot in power will soon find his punishment."

167
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,810
“It's never too late for a gentleman to take his revenge!"

168
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:51,020
Secretary office. How may I help you?

169
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:55,630
Secretary Song? He is not here right now.

170
00:14:57,410 --> 00:15:00,650
To confirm the meeting time with Interim CEO?

171
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:07,440
Hello, this is Secretary Song.

172
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:11,120
Yes. Wednesday afternoon at 3PM.

173
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,880
Ok. I got it. Thank you.

174
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:25,490
Maka Long. From this day on,

175
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:28,550
all the documents and phone calls in the secretary's office

176
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:32,050
are off-limits for you. Do you hear me?

177
00:15:38,450 --> 00:15:42,340
It's your working hours. Why are you here?<br>Go away now while William is still resting.

178
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:45,430
If he sees you, he'll definitely ask you<br> what's happening in the company.

179
00:15:45,430 --> 00:15:49,410
- There is one thing I must tell you.<br>- What is it?<br>- It's...

180
00:15:51,940 --> 00:15:54,620
Is this something I shouldn't know?

181
00:15:56,290 --> 00:15:58,180
I don't think this is a good idea.

182
00:15:58,180 --> 00:16:02,000
That's ok. There is nothing we can't let Katy know.

183
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,370
Tell us!

184
00:16:04,370 --> 00:16:09,500
I found out that General Manager Zhao and Shiji Bank's VIP service department

185
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:12,730
made an appointment to open CEO's safe.

186
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:15,300
Is this something strange? He is the Interim CEO.

187
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:18,030
He is given the power to do so.

188
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:20,390
But I don't know why, I just find it weird.

189
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:22,790
So I called and asked Secretary Wan.

190
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:29,750
He said, in the safe, there are all the operating-before-authorization agreements between Yi Shan and its collaborators.

191
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:34,800
In short, those are the original copies of the memos<br>that were given to you.

192
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:43,430
If General Manger Zhao gets hold of the information,<br>I'm afraid he might use it against William.

193
00:16:43,430 --> 00:16:44,950
I am going to scold him right now!

194
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:47,790
He has already made William this way,<br>what else does he want?

195
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:49,750
Calm down first. Don't act so impulsively!

196
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,390
How can I calm down?

197
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:53,210
Yi Shan is William's life.

198
00:16:53,210 --> 00:16:55,910
What does your dad want to achieve<br>by getting these documents?

199
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:57,930
He is already the Interim CEO.

200
00:16:57,930 --> 00:17:01,790
Even if he needs to call for a board meeting,<br>all the board members are on very good terms with him.

201
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,820
If they are to elect a new CEO,

202
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,740
your dad is very likely to get elected.

203
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:08,090
So why does he want to get these documents?

204
00:17:08,090 --> 00:17:11,500
There is more…<br>Recently I found out that

205
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:13,750
they opened another company.

206
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:17,770
That company's capital flows look very strange.

207
00:17:17,770 --> 00:17:21,550
Secretary Wan worries that, as the first step, Zhao wants to<br>completely defeat William

208
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,400
and make him unable to return to Yi Shan forever.

209
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:27,680
Next, he will drain Yi Shan's bank accounts.

210
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:32,340
So we definitely can't let him get hold of these documents,<br>otherwise we'll be doomed!

211
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:35,280
William?

212
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:43,250
I have to go to the office!

213
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:46,100
- Calm down!<br>- I'll definitely find a way to stop Daddy.

214
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,820
Go away, all of you!

215
00:17:47,820 --> 00:17:50,190
Maka Long, hold on to him.<br>I'm going to call for help.

216
00:17:50,190 --> 00:17:51,600
- Let me go!<br>- CEO, please calm down!

217
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:54,030
Problem… can't be solved this way.

218
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:56,100
Maka Long, let's go get the documents from the safe.

219
00:17:56,100 --> 00:17:58,090
- I don't believe I can't do anything. Let me go!<br>- Brother!

220
00:17:58,090 --> 00:18:01,060
Can't you focus on dealing with your<br>mental and physical health first?

221
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,990
I don't want to. I must protect Yi Shan.

222
00:18:02,990 --> 00:18:05,920
I am nothing if I can't protect Yi Shan.<br>Go away!

223
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:07,840
Don't be like this, please!

224
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:09,190
We'll definitely find a solution.

225
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:12,540
Scram! Go away!

226
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:14,960
You want to go, right? I'll come with you.

227
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:17,680
I will come with you. So please calm down.

228
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,470
Katy Zhao, don't do this.

229
00:18:19,470 --> 00:18:21,600
Don't always yield to him, ok?

230
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:24,040
William Yi! We won't leave you.

231
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:27,020
Even if you don't have Yi Shan, or if you're not CEO,

232
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:30,010
I believe Dad would rather use Yi Shan<br>in exchange for your health. Do you understand?

233
00:18:30,010 --> 00:18:32,240
I don't understand! I don't.

234
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:34,650
- Go away!<br>- Don't be like this.

235
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:37,310
Let me go! Let me…

